title: Learning shape combinations
content:
Hello, and thank you for taking part in this experiment.
In this experiment, we would like to study how people remember combinations of objects.

Please press 'g' to continue…

title: Learning shape combinations

content:

Pleae press 't' to continue…

title: Learning shape combinations
content:

Pleae press 't' to continue…
